---
title: Gravy-Smothered Pork Chops with Honey-Roasted Carrots & Zesty Couscous
description: We’re crazy for gravy around here—and you’re about to see why! A silky onion gravy enhanced with fresh thyme and enriched with beef and chicken stock is just what you want to spoon over savory seared pork chops. And yes, some of that savory goodness is bound to run over into your sides, but don’t you worry … our chefs designed it that way. If everything gets mixed up, it’s all gravy!
